dynamic response and tolerance is recommended if these agents are used together, and the dosage of one or both agents adjusted as necessary.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/75497/', '', 'Enalapril, Moexipril, Ramipril, Lisinopril, Perindopril, Bisoprolol, Benazepril, Quinapril, Trandolapril, Captopril, Fosinopril', 'Olmesartan, Azilsartan medoxomil, Candesartan, Eprosartan, Sacubitril', 1767369485);
